<section class="cover imagebg-hero height-60 text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
        <span class="landing-eyebrow text-white">A daily system for wellbeing</span>
        <h1 class="landing-title text-white">Build a life that feels lighter, calmer, and more meaningful</h1>
        <p class="lead mb-4 text-white opacity-100">MyDay helps you increase happiness by tracking mood, energy, gratitude, and direction in one place, so you can repeat what makes your days better.</p>
        <div class="landing-cta">
          <% if current_user %>
            <%= link_to "Go to Dashboard", dashboards_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary mr-2" %>
          <% else %>
            <%= link_to "Get Started for Free", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary mr-2" %>
            <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-outline-primary" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="space--sm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row text-center">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2 class="landing-section-title">A Practical Framework for Happiness</h2>
        <p class="landing-section-subtitle">The app turns vague self-improvement into a daily loop you can actually follow.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
      <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <i class="material-icons feature-icon">sentiment_very_satisfied</i>
          <h4 class="feature-title">Notice What Lifts You</h4>
          <p class="feature-text">Track mood over time and see which routines, people, and environments consistently improve your days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <i class="material-icons feature-icon">battery_charging_full</i>
          <h4 class="feature-title">Protect Your Energy</h4>
          <p class="feature-text">Measure energy alongside mood so you can catch burnout early and make better decisions before the day slips away.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <i class="material-icons feature-icon">favorite</i>
          <h4 class="feature-title">Practice Gratitude</h4>
          <p class="feature-text">End the day by naming what was good, supportive, or meaningful so attention shifts toward what is already working.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <i class="material-icons feature-icon">explore</i>
          <h4 class="feature-title">Stay Aligned</h4>
          <p class="feature-text">Use one meaningful daily challenge and reflection prompts to keep your time pointed at what matters most.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="space--sm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-10">
        <div class="happiness-loop">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="happiness-loop-step">
                <span class="loop-step-number">01</span>
                <h4>Check in</h4>
                <p>Score your mood, energy, and sense of alignment in under a minute.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="happiness-loop-step">
                <span class="loop-step-number">02</span>
                <h4>Name the friction</h4>
                <p>Identify the one challenge that would make tomorrow noticeably better.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="happiness-loop-step">
                <span class="loop-step-number">03</span>
                <h4>Capture the good</h4>
                <p>Write down what you are grateful for before your attention moves on.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="happiness-loop-step">
                <span class="loop-step-number">04</span>
                <h4>Adjust tomorrow</h4>
                <p>Use the reflection prompt to design a day that feels calmer and more satisfying.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="space--sm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row text-center mb-5">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2 class="landing-section-title">Meaningful Work Builds Alignment</h2>
        <p class="landing-section-subtitle">Alignment — how well your time matches your values — is one of the three pillars of your happiness score. Projects give that alignment somewhere to live.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p class="landing-section-text">
          Each project is an area of meaningful work. When you make progress inside it, you feel the day was well spent — and that moves your alignment score up.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">check_circle</i>
            <strong>Todos</strong> — clear, completable steps reduce mental load and give you a felt sense of progress
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">timer</i>
            <strong>Time tracking</strong> — see where your effort goes so your calendar reflects what actually matters to you
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">description</i>
            <strong>Blog posts</strong> — writing about your work reveals which kinds of effort bring energy and which drain it
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">book</i>
            <strong>Study materials</strong> — keep thinking organized so energy goes into work, not into finding things
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">link</i>
            <strong>Saved links</strong> — capture useful resources on the spot so your focus stays unbroken
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="project-showcase">
          <%= image_tag "project.png", class: "img-fluid rounded", alt: "Project Dashboard" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="space--sm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="landing-section-title">Daily Reflections That Improve Tomorrow</h2>
        <p class="landing-section-text">
          Build self-awareness by tracking the inputs that most strongly influence happiness:
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">mood</i>
            Daily mood and energy levels
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">star</i>
            Biggest challenges and achievements
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">school</i>
            Lessons learned each day
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">favorite</i>
            Daily gratitude practice
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="material-icons align-middle mr-2">trending_up</i>
            Progress over time with visual charts
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
        <div class="reflection-showcase">
          <%= image_tag "dashboard_page.png", class: "img-fluid rounded", alt: "Daily Reflections" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section text-center bg-dark text-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2 class="landing-section-title text-white">Ready to Build Happier Days on Purpose?</h2>
          <p class="landing-section-subtitle text-white opacity-75">Start tracking the habits, emotions, and reflections that genuinely improve your life.</p>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <% if current_user %>
              <%= link_to "Go to Dashboard", dashboards_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
            <% else %>
              <%= link_to "Start for Free", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
